match.name: Price Ball Busters PRS 1 day Feb 28th
match.about:
Regional PRS 1 day match. Gates open at 7am.  Site in 7:30am.  Match brief 8am.  

Venmo or cash payment is required before you will be able to shoot.

Venmo:   @Shaun-Haymore
